      "professional_reviews": {
        "summary": "Reviewers consistently call the F-PACE one of the most engaging-to-drive luxury crossovers, citing precise steering, well-tuned brakes, the smooth I6 MHEV powertrain, and the SVR's V8 character. The most common criticism is that the infotainment system and material quality lag newer rivals, and the base I4 P250 is the weakest powertrain choice. The MY26 'final year' status is widely acknowledged as the SUV concludes Jaguar's ICE era.",
